message: Starting critique review - gathering phase handover and agent findings

CRITIQUE SUBMITTED: Comprehensive senior developer review completed with 10 observations covering architectural concerns (schema transformation required, format inconsistency), praise (exceptional execution, metadata extraction), and strategic recommendations for Phase 2. Key findings: deliverables fully met, but critical schema mismatch between extracted content and study-site target format needs resolution before Phase 2 implementation.
